markets.guidance:
1x2(3 WAY)

This market has 3 possible outcomes at *Full Time.

The following options are available:

  •  Home WIN (1) bet wins if Home team wins the match. (e.g. the result of the match is 1:0 , 2:0, 2:1, etc.)
  •  Draw (X) bet wins if the match without winners. (e.g. the result of the match is 0:0 , 1:1, 2:2, etc.)
  •  Away WIN (2) bet wins if Away team wins the match. (e.g. the result of the match is 0:1 , 0:2, 1:2, etc.)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: 1x2
markets.title: 1,X,2

markets.guidance:
1x2 - Early Payout

This market has 3 possible outcomes at *Full Time.

The following options are available:

  •  Home WIN (1) bet wins if Home team wins the match or goes 2 goals ahead at any time during the match.
  •  Draw (X) bet wins if the match without winners. (e.g. the result of the match is 0:0 , 1:1, 2:2, etc.)
  •  Away WIN (2) bet wins if Away team wins the match or goes 2 goals ahead at any time during the match.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.

marketLabels.iconDesc: If the team you picked to win is two goals ahead at any time during the game, your bet gets settled as won, even if the opposing team eventually manages to equalize or even win the match!

markets.name: 1x2 - Early Payout

markets.guidance:
O/U

Predict if the total number of goals scored during the entire match is over/under a given line/spread indicated.*Full Time

0.5, 1.5, 2.5, 3.5, 4.5, 5.5

This market has 2 possible outcomes at *Full Time (FT) i.e. Over x.5 or Under x.5. For example (Ov/Un 2.5)

  •  Over 2.5 bet wins if there are 3 or more goals scored.(e.g. the result of match is 1:2 , 2:1, 2:2, 2:3, etc.)
  •  Under 2.5 bet wins if there are 2 or fewer goals scored.(e.g. the result of match is 0:0 , 1:0, 1:1, 0:1)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.

markets.guidance:
Double chance

A Double Chance bet allows you to cover two of the three possible outcomes in the match with one bet.*Full Time

The following options are available:

  •  1X bet wins if the result is either home win or draw then bets on this option are winners. (e.g. the result of match is 1:0 , 2:1, 0:0,1:1, etc.)
  •  X2 bet wins if the result is either draw or away win then bets on this option are winners. (e.g. The result of match is 0:0 , 1:1, 0:1,1:2, etc.)
  •  12 bet wins if the result is either home win or away win then bets on this option are winners. (e.g. the result of match is 1:0 , 0:1, 2:1,1:2, etc.)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: Double Chance
markets.title: 1X,12,X2

markets.guidance:
GG/NG

Predict if both teams will score at least one goal in the match.*Full Time

The following options are available:

  •  Yes(GG) bet wins if both teams scored in the match.(e.g. the result of the match is 1:1 , 2:1, 1:2, etc.)
  •  No(NG) bet wins if at least one team did not score in the match.(e.g. the result of the match is 0:0 , 0:1, 1:0, etc.)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: GG/NG
markets.title: GG,NG

markets.guidance:
GG/NG 2+

Predict if both teams will score at least 2 goals in the match.*Full Time

The following options are available:

  •  Yes(GG 2+) bet wins if both teams scored 2 goals in the match.(e.g. the result of the match is 2:2, 2:3, 3:2, etc.)
  •  No(NG 2+) bet wins if at least one team did not score 2 goals in the match.(e.g. the result of the match is 2:0, 2:1, 1:1, etc.)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: GG/NG 2+
markets.title: Yes,No

markets.guidance:
Draw no bet

Predict which team will win the match. If the teams draw, selection will be voided.*Full Time

The following options are available:

  •  Home bet wins if Home team wins the match.(e.g. the result of the match is 1:0, 2:0, 2:1, etc.)
  •  Away bet wins if Away team wins the match.(e.g. the result of the match is 0:1, 1:2, 0:2, etc.)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: DNB

markets.guidance:
Goal Streak 2+

Predict if any teams will score 2 or more goals in a row. *Full Time.

The following options are available:

  •  Yes bet wins if at least one team scored 2 goals in a row. (e.g. the result of the match is 2:0, 3:0, 4:0, etc.)
  •  No bet wins if no team scored 2 goals in a row. (e.g. the result of the match is 1:0, 0:1, 1:1, etc)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: Goal Streak 2+
markets.title: Yes,No

Predict if any teams will score 3 or more goals in a row. *Full Time.

The following options are available:

  •  Yes bet wins if at least one team scored 3 goals in a row. (e.g. the result of the match is 3:0, 4:0, 5:1, etc.)
  •  No bet wins if no team scored 3 goals in a row. (e.g. the result of the match is 2:0, 1:1, 2:1, etc)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.

  •  No bet wins if Home team not scored at least 2 goals in a row. (e.g. the result of the match is 1:0, 0:1, 1:1, etc)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.

markets.guidance:
Handicap

Predict the outcome of the match after given goals are added to the one of the teams, after the final score. (Imaginary goals only applicable in this market)*Full Time

Euro 1:0-Home team is getting advantage of 1 goal

  •  Home bet wins if Home team wins with any number of goals, or the match ends without winner.(e.g. the result of this match is 0:0, 1:0, 2:1, etc.)
  •  Draw bet wins if Away team wins with exactly 1 goal. (e.g. the result of this match is 0:1, 1:2, 4:5, etc.)
  •  Away bet wins if Away team wins with at least 2 goals difference.(e.g. the result of this match is 0:2, 1:3, 2:5, etc.)

Euro 0:2-Away team is getting advantage of 2 goals

  •  Home bet wins if Home team wins with 3 or more goals.(e.g. the result of this match is 3:0, 4:0, 4:1, etc.)
  •  Draw bet wins if Home team wins with exactly 2 goals.(e.g. the result of this match is 2:0, 3:1, 4:2, etc.)
  •  Away bet wins if Away teams wins the game, or loses with at most 1 goal.(e.g. the result of the match is 0:1, 2:1, 1:0, 2:2, etc.)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: Handicap
markets.title: Goals,1,X,2

markets.guidance:
Goals Range

Please select the range that you think will contain the final goal. If the final total goal is within the range of your choice, then you win.

For example:

Selections=Goals range 2-4
Won
Total goals(Result)= 3
Lost
Total goals(Result)= 5
markets.name: Goals Range
markets.title: All

markets.guidance:
Excluded Goals

Please choose which number you do not think will be the final goal. If the final goal of the game does not equal to the number you selected, then you win.

For example:

Selections=Excluded Goals 2
Won
Total goals(Result) 2
Lost
Total goals(Result)= 2

markets.guidance:
To qualify

Predict which team will be qualified to the next round.*Only Cup

The following options are available:

  •  Home bet wins if Home team is qualified to the next round.(e.g. the final result of the match is 1:0 , 2:0, 2:1, etc.)
  •  Away bet wins if Away team is qualified to the next round.(e.g. the final result of the match is 0:1 , 0:2, 1:2, etc.)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: To qualify

markets.guidance:
Winning method

Predict the winning team and winning method of a match. Please note match with multiple legs will consider a combined result of all legs. This bet is only available to those matches that potentially have overtime and penalty shootout.*only cup

The following options are available:

  •  Home regular time bet wins if Home wins at the regular time.
  •  Away regular time bet wins if Away wins at the regular time.
  •  Home overtime bet wins if Home wins at overtime.
  •  Away overtime bet wins if Away wins at overtime.
  •  Home penalties bet wins if Home wins at penalties.
  •  Away penalties bet wins if Away wins at penalties.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its regular time and overtime including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: Winning method

markets.guidance:
The Nth goal

Predict which team scores the Nth goal in the match.*Full time

The following options are available:

  •  Home bet wins if Home team scores the Nth goal in the macth.
  •  Away bet wins if Away team scores the Nth goal in the macth.
  •  None bet wins if there is no Nth goal in the match.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.

  •  Away bet wins if Away scores the last goal in the macth.
  •  None bet wins if there is no goal in the match.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.

  •  Away bet wins if Away team wins the match.(e.g. the result of the match is 0:1, 1:2, 0:2, etc.)

  •  Home bet wins if the Home team wins the match.(e.g. the result of the match is 1:0, 2:1, 2:0, etc.)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.

markets.guidance:
Winning margin

Predict by how many goals the winning team wins the match.*Full Time

The following options are available:

  •  Home by 1 bet wins if Home wins Away 1 goal.(e.g. the result of the match is 1:0,2:1,3:2, etc.)
  •  Home by 2 bet wins if Home wins Away 2 goals.(e.g. the result of the match is 2:0,3:1, 4:2, ect.)
  •  Home by 3+ bet wins if Home wins Away 3 or more goals.(e.g. the result of the match is 3:0, 4:0 ,4:1, etc.)
  •  Away by 1 bet wins if Away wins Home 1 goal.(e.g. the result of the match is 0:1,1:2,2:3, etc.)
  •  Away by 2 bet wins if Away wins Home 2 goals.(e.g. the result of the match is 0:2,1:3, 2:4, ect.)
  •  Away by 3+ bet wins if Away wins Home 3 or more goals.(e.g. the result of the match is 0:3, 0:4 ,1:4, etc.)
  •  Draw bet wins if the teams draw.(e.g. the result of the match is 0:0,1:1,2:2, etc.)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: Winning margin

markets.guidance:
Exact goals

Predict the exact total number of the goals at *Full Time.

The following options are available:

  •  0 bet wins when there is no goal scored in the match.(e.g. the result of match is 0:0)
  •  1 bet wins if there is exactly 1 goal in the match.(e.g. the result of match is 1:0 or 0:1)
  •  2 bet wins if there are exactly 2 goals in the match.(e.g. the result of match is 0:2, or 1:1, or 2:0)
  •  3 bet wins if there are exactly 3 goals in the match.(e.g. the result of match is 0:3, 1:2, 2:1, or 3:0)
  •  4 bet wins if there are exactly 4 goals in the match.(e.g. the result of match is 0:4, 1:3, 2:2,3:1 or 4:0)
  •  5 bet wins if there are exactly 5 goals in the match.(e.g. the result of match is 1:4, 2:3, 3:2,4:1, etc.)
  •  6+ bet wins if there are 6 or more goals in the match.(e.g. the result of match is 1:5, 2:4, 3:3,4:2, etc.)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: Exact goals

The following options are available:

  •  Odd bet wins if the match ends with an odd number of total goals - 1,3,5,7...(e.g. the result of this match is 1:0 , 1:2, 2:3, etc.)
  •  Even bet wins if the match ends with an even number of total goals -0,2,4,6,8...e.g. the result of this match is 0:0 , 1:1, 2:4, etc.)

Predict which team will score at least one goal in the match.*Full Time

The following options are available:

  •  None bet wins when neither team scores in the match.(e.g. the result of the match is 0:0)
  •  Only Home bet wins when only Home team scores in the match.(e.g. the result of the match is 1:0,2:0,3:0,etc.)
  •  Only Away bet wins when only Away team scores in the match.(e.g. the result of the match is 0:1,0:2,0:3,etc.)
  •  Both teams bet wins if both teams score in the match.(e.g. the result of the match is 1:1,2:1,1:2,etc.)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.

Correct score

Predict the correct score at the end of *Full Time.

The following options are available:

  •  0:0 bet wins if the match ends with 0:0.

    • ......

  •  2:1 bet wins if the match ends with 2:1.

    • ......

  •  Others bet wins if the match ends with any other score.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.

markets.guidance:
HT/FT Result

Predict the result of a match both at the 1st half time and full time.

The following options are available:

  •  1/1 bet wins if Home team leads after the 1st half and also wins the match.
  •  1/X bet wins if Home team leads after the 1st half and match ends in draw.
  •  1/2 bet wins if Home team leads after the 1st half and the Away team wins the match.
  •  X/1 bet wins if the 1st half ends in draw and the Home team wins the match.
  •  X/X bet wins if the 1st half ends in draw and also the match ends in draw.
  •  X/2 bet wins if the 1st half ends in draw and Away team wins the match.
  •  2/1 bet wins if Away team leads after the 1st half and Home team wins the match.
  •  2/X bet wins if Away team leads after the 1st half and match ends in draw.
  •  2/2 bet wins if Away team leads after the 1st half and also wins the match.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: HT/FT Result

markets.guidance:

Predict if there is overtime in the match and if there is a goal in overtime.*Overtime

The following options are available:

  •  No bet wins if there is no overtime in the match or there is no goal in overtime.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its Overtime including all injury and stoppage time.

Predict if the Home team scores more or less goals than the given line in the *First half.

0.5, 1.5, 2.5, 3.5

This market has 2 possible outcomes in the first half. i.e. Over x.5 or Under x.5. For example (Ov/Un 1.5)

  •  Over 1.5 bet wins if Home team scores 2 or more goals in the first half.
  •  Under 1.5 bet wins if Home team scores 1 or fewer goal in the first half.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its first half time including all injury and stoppage time.

markets.guidance:
Multigoals

Predict what is sum of goals at *full time.

The following options are available:

  •  1-2 bet wins if the total number of goals is 1 or 2.
  •  1-3 bet wins if the total number of goals is between 1-3.
  •  1-4 bet wins if the total number of goals is between 1-4.
  •  1-5 bet wins if the total number of goals is between 1-5.
  •  1-6 bet wins if the total number of goals is between 1-6.
  •  2-3 bet wins if the total number of goals is between 2-3.
  •  2-4 bet wins if the total number of goals is between 2-4.
  •  2-5 bet wins if the total number of goals is between 2-5.
  •  2-6 bet wins if the total number of goals is between 2-6.
  •  3-4 bet wins if the total number of goals is between 3-4.
  •  3-5 bet wins if the total number of goals is between 3-5.
  •  3-6 bet wins if the total number of goals is between 3-6.
  •  4-5 bet wins if the total number of goals is between 4-5.
  •  4-6 bet wins if the total number of goals is between 4-6.
  •  5-6 bet wins if the total number of goals is between 5-6.
  •  7+ bet wins if the total number of goals is 7 or more.
  •  No goal bet wins if there is no goal in the match.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: Multigoals

markets.guidance:
Multiscores

Predict what is the final result.*full time

The following options are available:

  •  1:0, 2:0 or 3:0 bet wins if the final result is 1:0, 2:0 or 3:0.
  •  0:1, 0:2 or 0:3 bet wins if the final result is 0:1, 0:2 or 0:3.
  •  4:0, 5:0 or 6:0 bet wins if the final result is 4:0, 5:0 or 6:0.
  •  0:4, 0:5 or 0:6 bet wins if the final result is 0:4, 0:5 or 0:6.
  •  2:1, 3:1 or 4:1 bet wins if the final result is 2:1, 3:1 or 4:1.
  •  1:2, 1:3 or 1:4 bet wins if the final result is 1:2, 1:3 or 1:4.
  •  3:2, 4:2, 4:3 or 5:1 bet wins if the final result is 3:2, 4:2, 4:3 or 5:1.
  •  2:3, 2:4, 3:4 or 1:5 bet wins if the final result is 2:3, 2:4, 3:4 or 1:5.
  •  Other Homewin bet wins if Home wins at other results.
  •  Other Awaywin bet wins if Away wins at other results.
  •  Draw bet wins if the teams draw.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.

HT FT Correct score

Predict the first half result and the final result at the end of the match among the ones proposed in the list. The first result relates to the first half of match and the second result relates to the end of match.

The following options are available:

  •  0:0 0:0 bet wins if the first half result is 0:0 and the full time result is 0:0.

    • ......

  •  1:1 2:1 bet wins if the first half result is 1:1 and the full time result is 2:1.

    • ......

  •  1:2 4+ bet wins if the first half result is 1:2 and the number of total goals at full time is 4 or more.(e.g. 1:2 1:3, 1:2 2:3, etc.)

    • ......

  •  4+ 4+ bet wins if the number of goals in the first half is 4 or more and the number of total goals at full time is 4 or more.(e.g. 2:2 2:3, 3:1 3:2, etc.)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.

Predict if the selected player will score at least one goal during the match and 1x2. *full time

The following options are available:

  •  {%player} & Home bet wins if the selected player scores at least one goal and Home team wins the match.
  •  {%player} & Draw bet wins if the selected player scores at least one goal and the teams draw.
  •  {%player} & Away bet wins if the selected player scores at least one goal and Away team wins the macth.
  •  Other bet wins if the selected player does not score.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.

Anytime goalscorer & correct score

Predict if the selected player will score at least one goal during the match and the correct socre. *full time

The following options are available:

  •  {%player} & 1:0 bet wins if the selected player scores at least one goal and the result of the match is 1:0.
  •  {%player} & 2:0 bet wins if the selected player scores at least one goal and the result of the macth is 2:0.

    • ......

  •  {%player} & 4:4 bet wins if the selected player scores at least one goal and the result of the match is 4:4.
  •  Other bet wins if there is any other results.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.

Predict if the selected player will score at least one goal during the match and the correct socre. *full time

The following options are available:

  •  {%player} & 1:0 bet wins if the selected player scores at least one goal and the result of the match is 1:0.
  •  {%player} & 2:0 bet wins if the selected player scores at least one goal and the result of the macth is 2:0.

    • ......

  •  {%player} & 4:4 bet wins if the selected player scores at least one goal and the result of the match is 4:4.
  •  Other bet wins if there is any other results.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.

Predict that the selected player will score the Nth goal of the match and the correct socre. *full time

The following options are available:

  •  Player & 1:0 bet wins if the selected player scores the Nth goal and the result of the match is 1:0.
  •  Player & 2:0 bet wins if the selected player scores the Nth goal and the result of the macth is 2:0.

    • ......

  •  Player & 4:4 bet wins if the selected player scores the Nth goal and the result of the match is 4:4.
  •  Other bet wins if there is any other results.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.

{!goalnr} goalscorer & 1x2

Predict that the selected player will score the Nth goal of the match and 1x2. *full time

The following options are available:

  •  {%player} & Home bet wins if the selected player scores the Nth goal and Home wins the match.
  •  {%player} & Draw bet wins if the selected player scores the Nth goal and the teams draw.
  •  {%player} & Away bet wins if the selected player scores the Nth goal and Away wins the match.
  •  Other bet wins if there is any other results.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.

markets.description: When will the 1st goal be scored (15 min interval)
markets.guidance:
When will the Nth goal be scored (15 min interval)

Predict when will the Nth goal be scored(an interval per 15 minutes).*Full Time

The following options are available(for example: the 2nd goal):

  •  1-15 bet wins if the 2nd goal is scored in between 1 to 15 minutes.
  •  16-30 bet wins if the 2nd goal is scored in between 16 to 30 minutes.
  •  31-45 bet wins if the 2nd goal is scored in between 31 to 45 minutes.
  •  46-60 bet wins if the 2nd goal is scored in between 46 to 60 minutes.
  •  61-75 bet wins if the 2nd goal is scored in between 61 to 75 minutes.
  •  76-90 bet wins if the 2nd goal is scored in between 76 to 90 minutes.
  •  None bet wins if there is no 2nd goal in the match.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: When will the {!goalnr} goal be scored (15 min interval)

markets.description: When will the 1st goal be scored (10 min interval)
markets.guidance:
When will the Nth goal be scored (10 min interval)

Predict when will the Nth goal be scored(an interval per 10 minutes).*Full Time

The following options are available(for example: the 2nd goal):

  •  1-10 bet wins if the 2nd goal is scored in between 1 to 10 minutes.
  •  11-20 bet wins if the 2nd goal is scored in between 11 to 20 minutes.
  •  21-30 bet wins if the 2nd goal is scored in between 21 to 30 minutes.
  •  31-40 bet wins if the 2nd goal is scored in between 31 to 40 minutes.
  •  41-50 bet wins if the 2nd goal is scored in between 41 to 50 minutes.
  •  51-60 bet wins if the 2nd goal is scored in between 51 to 60 minutes.
  •  61-70 bet wins if the 2nd goal is scored in between 61 to 70 minutes.
  •  71-80 bet wins if the 2nd goal is scored in between 71 to 80 minutes.
  •  81-90 bet wins if the 2nd goal is scored in between 81 to 90 minutes.
  •  None bet wins if there is no 2rd goal in the match.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: When will the xth goal be scored (10 min interval)

markets.guidance:
10 minutes - 1x2 from {from} to {to}

Predict which team will take the lead or draw during the specified 10 minutes.

The following options are available(for example: the first 10 minutes):

  •  Home bet wins if Home team takes the lead during the first 10 minutes.
  •  Draw bet wins if the teams draw during the first 10 minutes.
  •  Away bet wins if Away team takes the lead during the first 10 minutes.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its specified 10 minutes including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: 10 minutes-1x2 from {from} to {to}
